en.title: FE Country & State Licensees Signing Ceremony at FE's 1 Million QP Celebration Banquet MAEPS, 23rd May 2009.
en.content:
01 (State of) Arizona, USA - Mr. Arthur A. Bernardo.

02 Brunei - Mr. M. D. Menon.

03 (State of) California, USA - Mr Art & Mrs Grace Tuason (Representative).

04 (State of) Hawaii, USA - Mr Jimmy Dee. 

05 Hong Kong - Captain Eliseo Demafelis.

06 (State of) Illinois, USA - Mr. Ammon Bailey.

07 (State of) Kerala and Maharashtra, India - Dr. Jacob K. B. 

08 (State of) Karnataka, India - Mr. Thomas Fernandes. 

09 Nepal - Mr. Ramsharan Puri.

10 (State of) Nevada, USA - Mr. Benjamin M. Cuaresma Jr.

11 Switzerland - Mr Hugo Risi.

12 United Arab Emirates - Arthur Medina (Representative) (Including Gulf Countries Bahrain, Saudi Arabia, 
    Oman, Kuwait, Qatar).

13 Vietnam - Mr. Nguyen Duc Doan.

14 Zambia - Mr. Rajen Ranchhod.
